{"tid":819671,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"砌機麻煩，不如買notebook 🐵","createTime":"2018-09-15T03:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T14:17:41.000Z","uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"63a9b5dedf205eadd8393a1946dc243f1df5151f","tid":819671,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果砌機那麼麻煩，不然買notebook，但又容易壞掉不耐用，應該買哪樣好？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aff37247f3c7ee7bc4117705077cd1375667246","tid":819671,"uid":152500,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"cca8336ea0fbb6e9474a5d222c3e47021c0186bd","tid":819671,"uid":24211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"DELL枱機"},{"pid":"c4b7343bf32bd517aa01684fffbee214ff7cff80","tid":819671,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"你都低能 砌機同notebook 根本唔同定位"},{"pid":"8d4d054a82a7106fb042d80f27f0b28018b28dfd","tid":819671,"uid":55369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4b7343bf32bd517aa01684fffbee214ff7cff80","tid":819671,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"你都低能 砌機同notebook 根本唔同定位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"唔好怪佢弱智<br />\n<br />\nmacbook air 都可以同pro 比<br />\ndesktop 同notebook 比都唔出奇既"},{"pid":"6a7286748a27563a8aff4598f2444da252704f56","tid":819671,"uid":58321,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔子背後來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常的，無論是雌性騎着雄性或兩隻同性別的騎着大家。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。<br />\n<br />\n以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=327f15e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔兔面前打開手掌，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果主人和兔兔的關係好，牠會groom主人。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說，在牠面前打開手掌是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵會放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放姿勢同驚慌一樣，但驚慌時坐姿會蹲下。) 以下video 是主人要求兔兔groom 主人的例子：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=709da5c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a> <br />\n<br />\n有趣視頻: 兩隻兔子正在決定等級制度，但遇到困難。兔子A groom 兔子B, 但groom 了很久和等了很久還未得到回報(兔子B groom A作為回報)，所以發脾氣在2:08咬兔子B。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1b379f5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a> <br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔子的頸上來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bf8c5317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nN.B.: 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會參觀然後領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=94395de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a><br />\n<br />\n更多資訊：<a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2F&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=54a730b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2F&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5a870c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/</a>"},{"pid":"f7dd26fe98ced3a9bf79278a694410756148000c","tid":819671,"uid":143260,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"樓上兔仔條友做咩撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66659e7da2f05fb9c6ff11fc7347411227fe3f60","tid":819671,"uid":179274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e5e19ea77d219a3d1ce1043c56995f623dae774","tid":819671,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eda5e9cab90363797b9b1af0e544d6ba94965afe","tid":819671,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"而家砌機有得送上門，係煩在壞左唔識整"},{"pid":"0993f5e739b3a7099416f2d3cf8d2aaa4c06ac23","tid":819671,"uid":132894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e5e19ea77d219a3d1ce1043c56995f623dae774","tid":819671,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"講到好似notebook駁唔到mon咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fcd6fc1bc5b148257